title: Mr Kebab
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Pizza, Italian, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small pizza place with a vegan pizza and vegan pide section on the menu. Has vegan cheese, veggies, vegan sausage and un-marinated tofu. Limited seating; mainly take-away. Collaborates with the Danish Vegan Society.
